<section class="known-site-section" id="quickstart">
    <div class="known-site-section-head">
        <span>快速开始</span>
        <h2>几步启动 Known 示例项目</h2>
        <p>直接运行仓库中的示例工程，即可体验框架能力与插件化组织方式。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="known-site-grid known-site-grid-2">
        <article class="known-site-card">
            <h3>本地运行</h3>
            <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/known/Known.git
cd Known/Known.Server
dotnet run</code></pre>
        </article>
        <article class="known-site-card">
            <h3>安装包</h3>
            <pre><code>dotnet add package Known</code></pre>
            <p>随后在你的 Blazor 应用中接入 Known 组件、服务和扩展能力。</p>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
